> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event\"><code>pageshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\"><code>popstate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/rejectionhandled_event\"><code>rejectionhandled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\"><code>storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unhandledrejection_event\"><code>unhandledrejection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\"><code>unload</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplayactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayblur_event\"><code>vrdisplayblur</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplayconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydeactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplaydeactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydisconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplaydisconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Własność localStorage pozwala na dostęp do lokalnego&nbsp;obiektu <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\"><code>Storage</code></a>. localStorage jest podobne w swoich założeniach do&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\">sessionStorage</a>.</code>&nbsp;Różnica pomiędzy nimi polega na tym, że dane przechowywane w&nbsp;<code>localStorage</code>&nbsp;nie mają daty ważności, a dane przechowywane w&nbsp;<code>sessionStorage</code>&nbsp;usuwane są po zakończeniu danej sesji - czyli przy&nbsp;zamknięciu przeglądarki.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>myStorage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wartość","title":"Wartość","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Obiekt <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\"><code>Storage</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Poniższy kod uzyskuje dostęp do lokalnego obiektu&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\"><code>Storage</code></a>, należącego do&nbsp;obecnej domeny i dodaje do niego własność&nbsp;używająć metody&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>Storage.setItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'myCat'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Tom'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Notka</strong>: Pełny przykład znajdziesz w&nbsp;artykule&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Using the Web Storage API</a>&nbsp;.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikajca","title":"Specyfikajca","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarz</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-localstorage\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'localStorage' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">Unknown</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wsparcie_przeglądarek","title":"Wsparcie przeglądarek","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Pulpit</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Własność</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>localStorage</td>\n   <td>4</td>\n   <td>3.5</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>10.50</td>\n   <td>4</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>sessionStorage</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td>2</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>10.50</td>\n   <td>4</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Własność</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Podstawowe wspracie</td>\n   <td>2.1</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td>iOS 3.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>Sposób wsparcia&nbsp;dla&nbsp;<code>localStorage</code>&nbsp;i&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>sessionStorage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> różni się w zależności od przeglądarki. Tutaj znajdziesz <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://dev-test.nemikor.com/web-storage/support-test/\" rel=\" noopener\">szczegółowe dane na temat wsparcia poszczególnych przeglądarek dla obiektów Storage</a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect4\">\n<p><strong>Notka:</strong>&nbsp;Zaczynając od wersji iOS 5.1, Safari przetrzymuje dane&nbsp;<code>localStorage</code>&nbsp;w folderze&nbsp;<code>cache.</code>&nbsp;Folder ten&nbsp;poddawany jest okresowemu czyszczeniu,&nbsp;zazwyczaj, gdy w pamięci&nbsp;urządzenia&nbsp;kończy się miejsce. Tryb prywatny w mobilnej przeglądarce Safari blokuje również całkowicie możliwość zapisu do pamięci&nbsp;<code>localStorage</code>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_także","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Using the Web Storage API</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>LocalStorage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>SessionStorage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"składnia"},{"text":"Przykład","id":"przykład"},{"text":"Specyfikajca","id":"specyfikajca"},{"text":"Wsparcie przeglądarek","id":"wsparcie_przeglądarek"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_także"}],"summary":"Własność localStorage pozwala na dostęp do lokalnego obiektu Storage. localStorage jest podobne w swoich założeniach do sessionStorage. Różnica pomiędzy nimi polega na tym, że dane przechowywane w localStorage nie mają daty ważności, a dane przechowywane w sessionStorage usuwane są po zakończeniu danej sesji - czyli przy zamknięciu przeglądarki.","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Window.localStorage","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/window/localstorage","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/window/localstorage/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"window"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage","title":"Window.localStorage"}],"pageTitle":"Window.localStorage - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}